    <preface>
      <p>SPECIAL ISSUE<eol />Kenya Gazette Supplement No. 102 (Acts No. 9)<eol /><docTitle
          id="ActTitle">THE RETIREMENT BENEFITS (AMENDMENT)</docTitle>
        <eol /><docType>ACT</docType>, 2003<eol />No. <docNumber>8</docNumber> of 2003<eol />Date of
        Assent: <docDate date="2003-12-10">10th December, 2003</docDate><eol />Date of Commencement:
        19th December, 2003</p>
    </preface>
    <preamble id="preamble">
      <p>An Act of Parliament to amend the Retirement Benefits Act, 1997<eol />ENACTED by the
        Parliament of Kenya, as follows: -</p>
    </preamble>
    <body>
      <article id="art1">
        <num>1.</num>
        <heading>Short title.</heading>
        <clause id="art1-cla1">
          <content><p>This Act may be cited as the Retirement Benefits (Amendment) Act, 2003.</p></content>
        </clause>
      </article>
      <article id="art2">
        <num>2.</num>
        <heading>Amendment of <ref id="ref19" href="/ke/act/1997-08-22/3/eng/main#art2">section 2 of
            No3 of 1997</ref></heading>
        <clause id="art2-cla1">
          <content><p>The Retirement Benefits Act, 1997, in this Act referred to as the principal Act, is
            amended -</p>
          <list id="art2-cla1-lst1">
            <item id="art2-cla1-itma">
              <num>(a)</num>
              <p>by deleting the definition of "financial year" and <mod id="mod6"><ref id="ref2"
                    href="/ke/act/1997-08-22/3/eng/main">substituting</ref> therefor the following
                  new definition - "<quotedText id="mod6-qtd1">financial year" -<eol /> (a) in
                    relation to the Authority, has the meaning assigned to it in section 19'<eol />
                    (b) in relation to a scheme, means such accounting period as may be prescribed
                    in the scheme rules;</quotedText></mod></p>
            </item>
            <item id="art2-cla1-itmb">
              <num>(b)</num>
              <p>by <mod id="mod7"><ref id="ref20" href="/ke/act/1997-08-22/3/eng/main"
                  >inserting</ref> the following new definitions in their proper alphabetical
                  sequence - "<quotedText id="mod7-qtd1">pooled fund" means a fund established by a
                    limited liability company, other than an approved issuer, for purposes of
                    pooling scheme funds for collective investment;<eol />"statutory fund" has the
                    meaning assigned to it in <ref id="mod7-qtd1-ref1" href="/ke/act/xxxxxx">Cap.487
                      section 2 of the Insurance Act</ref>.</quotedText></mod></p>
            </item>
          </list></content>
        </clause>
      </article>
      <article id="art3">
        <num>3.</num>
        <heading>Amendment of <ref id="ref3" href="/ke/act/1997-08-22/3/eng/main#art22">section 22 of
            No. 3 of 1997</ref>.</heading>
        <clause id="art3-cla1">
          <content><p>Section 22 of the principal Act is amended <ref id="ref4"
              href="/ke/act/1997-08-22/3/eng/main#art22-cla3">in subsection (3)</ref>-</p>
          <list id="art3-cla1-lst1">
            <item id="art3-cla1-itma">
              <num>(a)</num>
              <p>by <mod id="mod8"><ref id="ref5" href="/ke/act/1997-08-22/3/eng/main#art22-cla3"
                    >deleting</ref> the word "<quotedText id="mod8-qtd1">two</quotedText>" and
                  substituting therefore the word "<quotedText id="mod8-qtd2"
                >one</quotedText>"</mod>;</p>
            </item>
            <item id="art3-cla1-itmb">
              <num>(b)</num>
              <p>by <mod id="mod9"><ref id="ref6" href="/ke/act/1997-08-22/3/eng/main#art22-cla3"
                    >inserting</ref> the words "<quotedText id="mod9-qtd1">at least</quotedText>"
                  immediately before the word "<quotedText id="mod9-qtd2"
              >once</quotedText>"</mod>.</p>
            </item>
          </list></content>
        </clause>
      </article>
      <article id="art4">
        <num>4.</num>
        <heading>Amendment of <ref id="ref7" href="/ke/act/1997-08-22/3/eng/main#art34">section 34 of
            No.3 of 1997</ref>.</heading>
        <clause id="art4-cla1">
          <content><p><ref id="ref8" href="/ke/act/1997-08-22/3/eng/main#art34">Section 34</ref> of the
            principal Act is amended -</p>
          <list id="art4-cla1-lst1">
            <item id="art4-cla1-itma">
              <num>(a)</num>
              <p>in <mod id="mod10"><ref id="ref9"
                    href="/ke/act/1997-08-22/3/eng/main#art34-cla2-itma">subsection (2)</ref>, by
                  deleting the words "<quotedText id="mod10-qtd1">balance sheet</quotedText>"
                  appearing in paragraph (a) and substituting therefor the words "<quotedText
                    id="mod10-qtd2">statement of assets and liabilities</quotedText>"</mod>;</p>
            </item>
            <item id="art4-cla1-itmb">
              <num>(b)</num>
              <p>by inserting the following proviso at the end of <mod id="mod1"><ref id="ref10"
                    href="/ke/act/1997-08-22/3/eng/main#art34-cla3">subsection (3)</ref> -
                    "<quotedText id="mod1-qtd1">Provided that the appointed auditor shall not be a
                    member, trustee or sponsor of the scheme</quotedText>"</mod>.</p>
            </item>
          </list></content>
        </clause>
      </article>
      <article id="art5">
        <num>5.</num>
        <heading>Amendment of <ref id="ref11" href="/ke/act/1997-08-22/3/eng/main#art37">section 37 of
            No.3 of 1997</ref>.</heading>
        <clause id="art5-cla1">
          <content><p>Section 37 of the principal Act is amended by inserting the following proviso at the
            end of <mod id="mod2"><ref id="ref13" href="/ke/act/1997-08-22/3/eng/main#art37-cla1"
                >subsection (1)</ref> - "<quotedText id="mod2-qtd1">Provided that a scheme with a
                fund value of five million Kenya shillings or less may invest up to one hundred per
                centum of its scheme funds in Government securities</quotedText>"</mod>.</p></content>
        </clause>
      </article>
      <article id="art6">
        <num>6.</num>
        <heading>insertion of <ref id="ref14" href="/ke/act/1997-08-22/3/eng/main#art54">section 54A
            in No. 3 of 1997</ref></heading>
        <clause id="art6-cla1">
          <content><p>The principal Act is amended by inserting the following new section immediately after
              <mod id="mod3"><ref id="ref15" href="/ke/act/1997-08-22/3/eng/main#art54">section
              54</ref> - <quotedStructure id="mod3-qtd1">
                <article id="mod3-qtd1-art54.a">
                  <num>54A</num>
                  <heading>Conduct of prosecutions.</heading>
                  <clause id="mod3-qtd1-art54.a-cla1">
                    <num>(1)</num>
                    <content><p>The Attorney-General may, pursuant to the provisions of the Criminal
                      Procedure Code, appoint public prosecutors for the purposes of cases arising
                      under this Act.</p></content>
                  </clause>
                  <clause id="mod3-qtd1-art54.a-cla2">
                    <num>(2)</num>
                    <content><p>The Authority shall, for the purposes of the Criminal Procedure Code, be
                      deemed to be a public authority.</p></content>
                  </clause>
                </article>
              </quotedStructure></mod></p></content>
        </clause>
      </article>
      <article id="art7">
        <num>7.</num>
        <heading>Amendment of <ref id="ref16" href="/ke/act/2002-12-12/5/eng/main#art311">section 311
            of Cap 486</ref></heading>
        <clause id="art7-cla1">
          <content><p>Section 311 of Companies Act is amended -</p>
          <list id="art7-cla1-lst1">
            <item id="art7-cla1-itma">
              <num>(a)</num>
              <p>in subsection (1), by inserting the following paragraph immediately after <mod
                  id="mod4"><ref id="ref17" href="/ke/act/2002-12-12/5/eng/main#art311-cla1-itmc"
                    >paragraph (c )</ref> - <quotedStructure id="mod4-qtd1">
                    <list id="mod4-qtd1-lst1">
                      <item id="mod4-qtd1-itmcA">
                        <num>(cA)</num>
                        <p>all retirement benefits contributions and vested benefits of any clerk or
                          servant of the company;</p>
                      </item>
                    </list>
                  </quotedStructure></mod></p>
            </item>
            <item id="art7-cla1-itmb">
              <num>(b)</num>
              <p>by deleting the operative paragraph of <mod id="mod5"><ref id="ref18"
                    href="/ke/act/2002-12-12/5/eng/main#art311-cla2">subsection (2)</ref> and
                  substituting therefor the following - "<quotedStructure id="mod5-qtd1">
                    <clause id="mod5-qtd1-cla2">
                      <num>(2)</num>
                      <content><p>Notwithstanding anything in paragraph (c) or (cA) of subsection (1), the
                        sum to which priority is to be given under these paragraphs shall not, in
                        the case of any claimant, exceed twenty thousand shillings:</p></content>
                    </clause>
                  </quotedStructure>"</mod>.</p>
            </item>
            </list></content>
        </clause>
      </article>
    </body>
